OL,2,MTiny Drones in the Big Top
OL,4,CLondon Aerospace
OL,5,CFri 21:40-22:40
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GReturning to Stage A for one evening
OL,9,Gonly, London Aerospace invite anyone
OL,10,Gof any skill level or equipment (or
OL,11,Gnone) to come and get involved. We'll
OL,12,Ghave video goggles you can ridealong
OL,13,Gthrough, radios and simulators to have
OL,14,Ga carefree go at trying your hand at
OL,15,Gflying. If you have anything suitable
OL,16,Gfor indoor flying and/or FPV, feel
OL,17,Gfree to bring it along - BUT please
OL,18,Gdon't power up any equipment on site
OL,19,Guntil you've been briefed and
OL,20,Gallocated a frequency. Our definition
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
